---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Kostis Dovelos">
  <section class="about-grid">
    <article class="prose" style="padding-top: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Hello</h2>
      <p>
        I'm a wireless systems architect and consulting engineer based in Athens, Greece. I help
        defense and telecom organizations design, implement, and deploy mission-critical wireless
        systems, from architecture definition and algorithm design down to SW/HW implementation
        and integration.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="prose">
      <h2>The short version</h2>
    </article>

    <ul class="timeline">
      <li>
        <span class="when">2026 - now</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Senior DSP &amp; Wireless Communications Engineer</strong>, KRUSH Labs. DSP,
          SDR development, and wireless communications engineering for next-generation UAV
          datalinks.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2026 - now</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Wireless Systems Architect</strong>, Dovelos Engineering. Independent
          consultancy helping defense and telecom organizations design, implement, and deploy
          mission-critical wireless systems.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2024 - 2026</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Senior Wireless Communications Engineer</strong>, Intracom Defense. PHY design
          of next-generation MANET radios for unmanned vehicles: waveform and modem design, MIMO,
          channel coding, link adaptation, LPD/LPI.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2022 - 2024</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Antenna Engineer</strong>, Meta Materials Inc. Metamaterial-based solutions
          for 5G mmWave coverage; evolutionary optimization of anomalous reflectors.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2021 - 2022</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Postdoctoral Research Fellow</strong>, Queen's University Belfast.
          Superdirectivity for energy-efficient mmWave/sub-THz massive MIMO (ERC project
          BEATRICE).
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2017 - 2021</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Doctoral Researcher</strong>, Universitat Pompeu Fabra, Barcelona. Novel PHY concepts for 6G:
          ultra-massive MIMO, intelligent reflecting surfaces, interference alignment.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2015 - 2016</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Research Intern</strong>, CTTC, Barcelona. Implemented a slotted ALOHA
          network using LoRa radios and STM32 microcontrollers.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2014 - 2015</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Graduate Research Assistant</strong>, EPFL, Lausanne. Investigated the
          finite-length performance of irregular repetition slotted ALOHA (IRSA).
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <section class="side-projects">
      <article class="prose">
        <h2>AI Side Projects</h2>
        <p>
          In my spare time, I apply AI to problems that carry personal and societal weight. If
          you're interested in contributing, feel free to
          <a href="mailto:konstantinos.dovelos@gmail.com">drop me a line</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
      <ul class="project-index">
        <li>
          <h2><a href="https://pyxida.io">Pyxida</a></h2>
          <p class="meta">health · cardiology · 2026</p>
          <p>
            A personal companion that helps adults with congenital heart disease (CHD) navigate
            daily life with confidence and clarity. It keeps your whole cardiac story in one
            place: records explained in plain language, echo findings tracked over time, and
            heart-rate zones calibrated to you, not population averages.
          </p>
          <p class="project-link"><a href="https://pyxida.io">pyxida.io →</a></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>FindMyHeart</h2>
          <p class="meta">health · metabolic · 2026</p>
          <p>
            A cardiometabolic companion built for what generic fitness apps miss. It
            synthesizes your medical records and medication profile with real-time wearable
            data, delivering clinically contextualized feedback and personalized lifestyle
            interventions. Developed during LifeHack Athens 2026, a 36-hour life sciences
            hackathon at the heart of Panathēnea.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2>birdii</h2>
          <p class="meta">news · llms · 2025</p>
          <p>
            An AI-native news app that redefines how we engage with news. Instead of static
            headlines, birdii turns each article into something you can interact: summaries,
            additional background information for unfamiliar topics, and a conversational Q&amp;A
            that lets you ask follow-up questions and dig as deep as you want.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </section>
</Base>
